    \"name\": \"How can I find the nearest location to me?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"To find the nearest location, you can visit our website or use a search engine to locate Apex Fitness Studio near you.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"What is the difference between personal training and group classes at Apex Fitness Studio?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Personal training offers one-on-one instruction tailored to your goals, while group classes provide a social environment for fitness enthusiasts to work out together.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"How can I book a session with an instructor?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"You can book a session by calling our office or visiting our website to schedule an appointment with an available instructor.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"What amenities does Apex Fitness Studio offer?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Apex Fitness Studio provides state-of-the-art equipment, comfortable workout areas, and a variety of classes designed for all fitness levels.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n  </script>\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"speakable\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SpeakableSpecification\",\n    \"cssSelector\": [\n      \"#hero h1\",\n      \"#hero p\",\n      \".faq-answer\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n  </script>\n</head>\n<body class=\"min-h-screen bg-white\">\n\n<header class=\"bg-gray-800 text-white\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n    <nav class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\">\n      <div class=\"flex-shrink-0\">\n        <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-white text-lg font-semibold\">Apex Fitness Studio</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"hidden md:block\">\n        <div class=\"ml-4 flex items-center space-x-4\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium\">Home</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-green-500\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex items-center justify-between text-white\">\n      <h2 id=\"hero-headline\" class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl\">Train Like a Champion</h2>\n      <p id=\"hero-subtitle\" class=\"mt-2 max-w-md text-xl text-gray-100\">Empower Your Journey to Fitness</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<section class=\"bg-white py-10\" id=\"about-us\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8\">About Us</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-center mb-8\">Learn more about our mission and team at Apex Fitness Studio.</p>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center\">\n      <img src=\"/path/to/about-us-image.jpg\" alt=\"Apex Fitness Studio Team\" class=\"w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 mb-8 md:mb-0 rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover\" aria-label=\"Apex Fitness Studio Team\">\n      <div class=\"w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-center\">At Apex Fitness Studio, we believe in empowering individuals to reach their full potential through challenging and inspiring fitness programs. Our mission is to provide a safe, supportive environment where members can achieve their fitness goals under the guidance of experienced professionals.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"services\" class=\"bg-gray-100 py-20\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8\">Our Services</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-center mb-16 max-w-xl mx-auto\">Explore the range of fitness programs and services offered at Apex Fitness Studio.</p>\n    <ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n      <li class=\"bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 text-center\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4\">Personal Training</h3>\n        <p class=\"mb-4\">Get one-on-one attention with a certified personal trainer.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded\">Learn More</a>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 text-center\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4\">Group Classes</h3>\n        <p class=\"mb-4\">Join a variety of group classes to stay motivated and engaged.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded\">Learn More</a>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 text-center\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4\">Nutrition Consultations</h3>\n        <p class=\"mb-4\">Get personalized nutrition advice to support your fitness goals.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded\">Learn More</a>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"bg-gray-100 py-20 text-center\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\" aria-label=\"What Our Members Say\">What Our Members Say</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-lg mb-8\" aria-label=\"Read testimonials from our satisfied members\">Read testimonials from our satisfied members.</p>\n    <div class=\"testimonial-slider\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-md\">\n        <blockquote class=\"text-gray-700 font-medium mb-4\" aria-label=\"Apex Fitness Studio has transformed my fitness journey!\">Apex Fitness Studio has transformed my fitness journey!</blockquote>\n        <cite class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\" aria-label=\"John Doe\">John Doe</cite>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-md\">\n        <blockquote class=\"text-gray-700 font-medium mb-4\" aria-label=\"The personal training sessions were incredibly beneficial.\">The personal training sessions were incredibly beneficial.</blockquote>\n        <cite class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\" aria-label=\"Jane Smith\">Jane Smith</cite>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"bg-gray-900 text-white py-24 text-center\">\n  <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\" aria-label=\"Join Us Today!\">Join Us Today!</h2>\n  <p class=\"text-lg mb-8\" aria-label=\"Sign up for a free consultation and start your fitness journey with Apex Fitness Studio.\">Sign up for a free consultation and start your fitness journey with Apex Fitness Studio.</p>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-6 py-3 bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold rounded hover:bg-blue-700\" aria-label=\"Get Started\">Get Started</a>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"blog\" class=\"bg-gray-100 py-24\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center\">Blog</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-lg text-center mb-12\">Stay informed about fitness tips, nutrition advice, and studio updates.</p>\n    <ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n      <li aria-label=\"Blog Post 1\" class=\"bg-white shadow rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"block\">\n          <img src=\"placeholder.jpg\" alt=\"Fitness Tip\" class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\">\n          <div class=\"p-6\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Title of Post 1</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700\">Short description of the post...</p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      <li aria-label=\"Blog Post 2\" class=\"bg-white shadow rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"block\">\n          <img src=\"placeholder.jpg\" alt=\"Nutrition Advice\" class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\">\n          <div class=\"p-6\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Title of Post 2</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700\">Short description of the post...</p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      <li aria-label=\"Blog Post 3\" class=\"bg-white shadow rounded-lg overflow-hidden\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"block\">\n          <img src=\"placeholder.jpg\" alt=\"Studio Updates\" class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\">\n          <div class=\"p-6\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Title of Post 3</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700\">Short description of the post...</p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"bg-gray-100 py-24\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8\" id=\"contact-title\">Contact Us</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-lg text-center mb-12\" id=\"contact-description\">Get in touch with us for any inquiries or to book a session.</p>\n    <form action=\"#\" method=\"POST\" class=\"max-w-md mx-auto\">\n      <div class=\"mb-4\">\n        <label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2\">Name</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required class=\"shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"mb-4\">\n        <label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2\">Email</label>\n        <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required class=\"shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"mb-4\">\n        <label for=\"phone\" class=\"block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2\">Phone</label>\n        <input type=\"tel\" id=\"phone\" name=\"phone\" required class=\"shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"mb-4\">\n        <label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2\">Message</label>\n        <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required rows=\"6\" class=\"shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\"></textarea>\n      </div>\n      <button type=\"submit\" class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline\">Send</button>\n    </form>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"bg-white py-6\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center\" id=\"faqs\">FAQs</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-lg text-center mb-10\" id=\"faq-description\">Find answers to common questions about Apex Fitness Studio.</p>\n    <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"accordionExample\">\n      <div class=\"card border-0 rounded shadow-sm mb-4\">\n        <div class=\"card-header bg-gray-200 p-4\" id=\"headingOne\">\n          <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-link text-dark\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"collapseOne\">\n              What types of classes do you offer?\n            </button>\n          </h5>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordionExample\">\n          <div class=\"card-body text-gray-700\">\n            We provide a variety of group classes including cardio, strength training, and flexibility exercises.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"card border-0 rounded shadow-sm mb-4\">\n        <div class=\"card-header bg-gray-200 p-4\" id=\"headingTwo\">\n          <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-link text-dark collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapseTwo\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapseTwo\">\n              Do you have personal training sessions?\n            </button>\n          </h5>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"collapseTwo\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"headingTwo\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordionExample\">\n          <div class=\"card-body text-gray-700\">\n            Yes, we offer personalized training sessions to help you achieve your fitness goals.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n  <section id=\"faq\" class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n    <details class=\"border-b border-gray-200 py-4\">\n      <summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800\">What services does Apex Fitness Studio offer?</summary>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer mt-2 text-gray-600\">Apex Fitness Studio provides a variety of fitness services, including personal training, group classes, and wellness programs.</p>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"border-b border-gray-200 py-4\">\n      <summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800\">How can I find the nearest location to me?</summary>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer mt-2 text-gray-600\">To find the nearest location, you can visit our website or use a search engine to locate Apex Fitness Studio near you.</p>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"border-b border-gray-200 py-4\">\n      <summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800\">What is the difference between personal training and group classes at Apex Fitness Studio?</summary>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer mt-2 text-gray-600\">Personal training offers one-on-one instruction tailored to your goals, while group classes provide a social environment for fitness enthusiasts to work out together.</p>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"border-b border-gray-200 py-4\">\n      <summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800\">How can I book a session with an instructor?</summary>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer mt-2 text-gray-600\">You can book a session by calling our office or visiting our website to schedule an appointment with an available instructor.</p>\n    </details>\n    <details class=\"border-b border-gray-200 py-4\">\n      <summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800\">What amenities does Apex Fitness Studio offer?</summary>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer mt-2 text-gray-600\">Apex Fitness Studio provides state-of-the-art equipment, comfortable workout areas, and a variety of classes designed for all fitness levels.</p>\n    </details>\n  </section>\n</body>\n</html>",
